OL,3,CAurigny to investigate alleged
OL,4,Cdefamatory comments
OL,6,FGuernsey's airline Aurigny has
OL,7,Flaunched an investigation after a
OL,8,Fstaff member allegedly referred to the
OL,9,Fairline's wheelchair customers as
OL,10,F"lame and lazy".
OL,12,FThe comments came to light from an
OL,13,Fanonymous whistleblower who alleges
OL,14,Fthey were made on Wednesday 4
OL,15,FSeptember during a meeting with senior
OL,16,Fmanagement.
