OL,3,CAurigny to investigate alleged
OL,4,Cdefamatory comments
OL,6,FDuring a discussion about wheelchair
OL,7,Fpassengers, a member of staff
OL,8,Fallegedly referred to them as "lame
OL,9,Fand lazy", adding that half of
OL,10,Fwheelchair passengers did not need
OL,11,Fwheelchairs.
OL,13,FAt the same recent board meeting,
OL,14,Fanother senior figure was allegedly
OL,15,Fheard saying "Leave them and let them
OL,16,Fburn" when asked how to help disabled
OL,17,Fcustomers in the case of a fire.
