OL,3,CAurigny to investigate alleged
OL,4,Cdefamatory comments
OL,6,FThe whistleblower states: "I was in
OL,7,Fthe unfortunate position of listening
OL,8,Fto a Teams call last week with
OL,9,Fnumerous senior management present.
OL,11,F"This is absolutely disgusting, and I
OL,12,Fwas shocked to my core at what I was
OL,13,Fhearing from both of them. I trust a
OL,14,Fthorough investigation will be carried
OL,15,Fout."
OL,17,FDr Rob Harnish, Managing Director at
OL,18,FGuernsey-based disability charity Ron
OL,19,FShort Centre (UnLtd), hopes any
OL,20,Finvestigation is "handled sensitively".
