OL,3,CAurigny to investigate alleged
OL,4,Cdefamatory comments
OL,6,FWhile he wouldn't comment on specific
OL,7,Fallegations, he explains: "What we
OL,8,Fwant is for people who may have made
OL,9,Fcomments like this to actually
OL,10,Funderstand better what they've said.
OL,12,F"So many of us are upset. The idea is
OL,13,Falways to decrease the amount of
OL,14,Fignorance in society and to create a
OL,15,Fgreater cohesive community."
OL,17,FIn a statement, Aurigny says it is
OL,18,Fdealing with the allegations and will
OL,19,Fconsider what action, if any, is
OL,20,Fappropriate.
